<Layout title="Human-Centered ML | Harutyun Harry Ilanyan">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Educational Equity Analytics Platform</h1>
    
    <div class="alert alert-success mb-8">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
      </svg>
      <span>This project has been successfully completed with significant positive impact.</span>
    </div>

    <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    <p>
      A human-centered data science platform analyzing dual-enrollment program accessibility and outcomes, built with modern 
      web technologies and focused on positive societal impact. This project demonstrates how machine learning can prioritize 
      human needs, values, and interactions while promoting fairness and accessibility.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Comprehensive analysis of dual-enrollment program data</li>
      <li>Interactive dashboards for stakeholder insights</li>
      <li>Equity-focused metrics and evaluation frameworks</li>
      <li>Accessibility-first design principles</li>
      <li>Real-time reporting and visualization tools</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Technical Stack</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6 not-prose">
      <div class="badge badge-primary">Python</div>
      <div class="badge badge-secondary">JavaScript</div>
      <div class="badge badge-accent">Data Visualization</div>
      <div class="badge badge-info">React</div>
      <div class="badge badge-success">Django</div>
      <div class="badge badge-warning">PostgreSQL</div>
    </div>

    <h2>Impact & Results</h2>
    <p>
      The platform has successfully provided insights into educational equity patterns, helping institutions identify and 
      address barriers to dual-enrollment program participation. The human-centered approach ensures that data-driven 
      decisions prioritize student welfare and educational accessibility.
    </p>

    <h2>Research Contributions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Novel approaches to educational data analysis</li>
      <li>Framework for equity-focused machine learning applications</li>
      <li>Best practices for human-centered data science</li>
      <li>Methodology for stakeholder-inclusive system design</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="flex gap-4 mt-8 not-prose">
      <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-outline">‚Üê Back to Projects</a>
      <a href="mailto:harry_ila@berkeley.edu" class="btn btn-primary">Contact for Collaboration</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>